** Write a java program to create an array and give options to
user to perform linear search and binary search.
Give options as follows:
1. Press 1 to perform linear search
2. Press 2 to perform binary search
Note: Both searching logics should be present in the different
static methods as shown below:
1. Linear Search – linearSearch()
2. Binary Search – binarySearch()
Note: Binary search should be performed only if the array is in
sorted order otherwise print-”Enter the array in sorted order”